title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 30% Off Vapid Stanier LE Cruiser
content:
Warstock Cache & Carry is offering a 30% discount this week on the Vapid Stanier LE Cruiser Law Enforcement Vehicle. Unlock the ability to purchase your own off-the-books version of this LSPD pursuit fleet staple after scoping out the Police Station during The Gangbanger Robbery. Get the Stanier LE Cruiser's Trade Price by finding a piece of evidence at a Crime Scene.

Plus, use this Law Enforcement Vehicle to clean up the streets in Dispatch Work, courtesy of Vincent Effenburger.
